  // reset R3
  if (S2 < R2)

    S2 = R2;
  }
  else
  {

  }
  R2 = 0;
  C2 = C2 + 1;
  // reset R1
  // reset R0
}
resetPlaceHolder_2(); -> {
  // reset R3
  // reset R2
  if (S1 < R1)
  {
    S1 = R1;
  }
  else
  {
    ;
  }
  R1 = 0;
  C1 = C1 + 1;
  if ((j < 1) || (j == 1))
  {
    if (S0 < R0)
    {
      S0 = R0;
    }
    else
    {
      ;
    }
    R0 = 0;
    C0 = C0 + 1;
  }
  else
  {
    if ((j < 3) || (j == 3))
    {
      // reset R0
    }
    else
    {
      if ((j < 4) || (j == 4))
      {
        if (S0 < R0)
        {
          S0 = R0;
        }
        else
        {
          ;
        }
        R0 = 0;
        C0 = C0 + 1;
      }
      else
      {
        // reset R0
      }
    }
  }
}
use R chunk -> if ((j < 3) || (j == 3))
{
  if ((j < 0) || (j == 0))
  {
    R0 = R0 + chunk;
  }
  else
  {
    if ((j < 2) || (j == 2))
    {
      R3 = R3 + chunk;
    }
    else
    {
      R0 = R0 + chunk;
    }
  }
}
else
{
  R2 = R2 + chunk;
}

use R rep -> R1 = R1 + rep;

(let ((a!2 (< a!1 (+ tokens (* tokens (+ years months)))))
      (a!3 (= a!1 (+ tokens (* tokens (+ years months))))))
  (not (or a!2 a!3)))))

(check-sat)
(get-model)

      D0 = D0 + 1;

        {

        }
        else
        {

          {

          }
          else
          {

          }
        }
      }

      {
        D2 = D2 + chunk;
      }

        D1p = D1;
        D1 = 0;
        C1 = C1 + 1;
      }
      else
      {

      }
    }
    D0 = D0 + 1;
  }

    and temporarily modify /proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern, like so:

    echo core >/proc/sys/kernel/core_pattern
